label: SITENUMBER
description: This field stores a credit union-defined code identifying a site to which a vendor delivers cash orders.

label: SITENAME
description: This field stores a descriptive name for the site.

label: EXTRAADDRESS
description: This field stores an extra address line for the site's deliveries.

label: STREET
description: This field stores the street address for the site's deliveries.

label: CITY
description: This field stores the city for the site's delivery address.

label: STATE
description: This field stores the state for the site's delivery address.

label: ZIPCODE
description: This field stores the ZIP Code for the site's delivery address.

label: FAXPHONE
description: This field stores the phone number for the site's fax machine.

label: SITECONTACTNAME
description: This field stores the name of the contact person for this site.

label: CONTACTPHONE
description: This field stores the phone number of the site's contact person.

label: SITEID
description: This field stores the identifier the BillMe system uses to uniquely identify a site.

label: SITESETTLESHAREID
description: This field stores the ID of the share that the corporate interface debits for the total amount of the cash order.

label: CLOSEDATE
description: This field stores the date the site was closed.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: This field stores the system date in this field when you create, change, or save the Site record. Sometimes the system updates this field because the record was saved, even though there may not be any actual changes in the record.

label: LOCATOR
description: This field stores a unique number within each Preference record set that can be used as a unique identification of this record.
